  <ul>
    <li><b>DR. MIRRET</b> (Post Doctor Research Fellow, Harvard Medical School)</li>
    <li><b>DR. Dian Zeng</b> (Post Doctor Research Fellow, Harvard Medical School)</li>
  </ul>
</div>
<div class="home-block-info">
  <h2>Curriculum</h2>
  <div>
    We involve aspiring and established participants with ideas and can help them navigate their own professional and private world. GT participants are continually promoting research and innovation to foster deeper understanding and mobilize meaningful action.
    <div class="home-block-info__button-link">
      <%= link_to 'Read Full Curriculum', curriculum_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg", role: "button" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
